Juan Quarterone Carbone (born 28 May 1935) is a former Argentine football midfielder. Nickname El Brujo (The Wizard) he played in Argentina and El Salvador. After retiring as a player he coached a number of teams in El Salvador and the El Salvador national team. 
I read the paragraph on http://wikipedia.org
